      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CHOCOLATE'S CAN (2) has a strong winning strike-rate over this track and trip with five wins and a placing from nine tries. Missed the frame latest (19.96) when fourth over 340m at Hobart in a Grade 4. Expected to be in the finish. YES EILEEN (1) is a well performed sprinter ideally suited at the shorter trips. Finished seventh latest over 278m at this track (16.74) in a Grade 4. Solid record here at the distance winning four races. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Can measure up this time. KIWI ICE CUBE (5) is a capable type and proved too strong last time to win by 1.3 lengths at Hobart in a handy 19.40 beating You Who. Should feature again. HOW WE GO (3) is worth another chance despite missing the top-three here most recently.",
